Next to her grandparents graves...[p]
Many people in black have gathered.[p]
The sobbing of the people dressed in mourning clothes can be heard.[p]
Everyone is familiar.[p]
Her mother and father...[p]
Her three year younger sister...[p]
"What's wrong?[p]
Did something happen?"[p]
None of them answer.[p]
The police chief of Brahms...[p]
Fellow officers...[p]
And Sally...[p]
"Hey, Sally?[p]
Who passed away?"[p]
None of them answer.[p]


