The sacred ceremony is proceeding without delay.[p]
A magnificent casket is brought out by several men, and then it is gently lowered into a hole that was prepared in advance.[p]
Sally is whispering to Cybil's mother in a low voice.[p]
"I told her just think about what might happen...[p]
I recommended that she use a car for transportation.[p]
When pulling over violators, many accidents have happened...[p]
I just cannot believe that this could have happened to her..."[p]
Sally says this and then falls silent.[p]
"What?[p]
What are you saying?[p]
I am right here.[p]
Notice me..."[p]
Cybil tries as hard as she can to try and make someone notice her, but no matter what she does no one does.[p]
Her name has been engraved on the tombstone.[p]
"Am I dead?[p]
Am I dead?[p]
Someone tell me..."[p]


