Between the people dressed in black...[p]
There is a girl wearing a white one piece dress standing on the dark green grass, only half visible.[p]
She is just a figure, and only half of her face can be seen, but it is a familiar one.[p]
Everything becomes bathed in white.[p]
The girl's face sways as if it were floating in the air.[p]
And then, the girl softly calls Cybil's name.[p]
Before long, nothing else appeared in Cybil's eyes.[p]


